---
import NewsletterSignup from '~/components/common/newsletterSignup';
import PageLayout from '~/layouts/PageLayout.astro';
---

<PageLayout>
  <div class="text-justify mb-10 max-w-none">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-6">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p class="text-sm text-default mb-6">
      <strong>Effective Date:</strong> July 24, 2025
    </p>

    <p class="mb-6">
      This Privacy Policy describes how your personal data is collected and used when you visit and interact with this
      website ("Website").
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Owner and Data Controller</h2>
    <p class="mb-2"><strong>Name:</strong> Daniel Garcia</p>
    <p class="mb-2"><strong>Website:</strong> daniel.es</p>
    <p class="mb-6"><strong>Contact Email:</strong> hello@daniel.es</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">What Data We Collect</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      The only personal data this Website collects is your email address, which you provide when signing up for our
      newsletter.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Why We Collect Your Data</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Your email is collected solely to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li>Send you occasional newsletters or updates you've subscribed to.</li>
      <li>Manage your subscription preferences.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Legal Basis for Processing (EU Visitors)</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">Under the General Data Protection Regulation (GDPR), we process your personal data based on:</p>
    <p class="mb-4">Your consent when you voluntarily provide your email address to subscribe.</p>
    <p class="mb-6">
      You can withdraw your consent at any time by unsubscribing via the link in any email we send you or by contacting
      us.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">How We Store and Protect Your Data</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      Your data is securely stored by our email service provider (Loops). We take appropriate security measures to
      prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, or modification of your data.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Who We Share Your Data With</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We do not sell or rent your personal data. Your data is only shared with trusted third-party services that help us
      operate this Website (e.g., email newsletter software), and only for the purposes outlined above.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">How Long We Keep Your Data</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">We retain your email address until:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-6">
      <li>You unsubscribe from the newsletter, or</li>
      <li>You request deletion of your data.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Your Data Rights (Under GDPR)</h2>
    <p class="mb-4">If you are located in the EU/EEA, you have the right to:</p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-6 mb-4">
      <li>Access the personal data we hold about you.</li>
      <li>Request correction or deletion of your data.</li>
      <li>Withdraw consent at any time.</li>
      <li>Lodge a complaint with a data protection authority.</li>
    </ul>
    <p class="mb-6">To exercise any of these rights, contact us at [your@email.com].</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Cookies</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">This Website does not use cookies or trackers to collect personal data.</p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Changes to This Privacy Policy</h2>
    <p class="mb-6">
      We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The latest version will always be available on this page.
    </p>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Contact Us</h2>
    <p class="mb-2">For any questions or concerns, contact:</p>
    <p class="mb-2">Daniel Garcia</p>
    <p class="mb-2">gdpr@daniel.es</p>
    <p class="mb-6">Spain</p>
  </div>

  <NewsletterSignup />
</PageLayout>
